response.overview: This is the story of two brothers who grew up in the mountains of New England in the little town of Unity, NH. Their parents, Bev & Garry, met when Garry sold Bev some marijauna back in 1972. So, needless to say, their children were destined for greatness... or, madness. One thing was for sure, their lives would not be normal. One such thing was their odd obsession with independent music.
response.title: Anthem Of The Underground
